{"event": "listing", "data": {"url": "https://www.propertyguru.com.sg/listing/demo-tiong-bahru", "title": "Heritage 2BR at Tiong Bahru Road \u2014 Walking Distance to MRT", "address": "Tiong Bahru Road, Singapore", "price_sgd": 1320000, "bedrooms": 2, "sqft": 818, "raw_copy": "A rare chance to own in one of Singapore's most beloved heritage estates. This 2-bedroom apartment along Tiong Bahru Road is a comfortable 10 min walk to Tiong Bahru MRT, perfect for owner-occupiers who enjoy a stroll. A 14 min drive gets you to Raffles Place in light traffic. The neighbourhood offers a dense cluster of amenities \u2014 caf\u00e9s, bakeries, and a well-loved wet market \u2014 within 10 minutes on foot. A 12 min walk brings you to Zhangde Primary School, a convenient option for families. Street view captures the iconic art-deco shophouses that define the area; see for yourself before you visit. 818 sqft, well-kept, asking S$1,320,000. Honest listing \u2014 come see the place.", "photos": [], "t": 1777016649.925323, "seq": 2}}
